snippet.title: Blunderbubb! - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Check out the launch trailer for Smiling Quarter's first mobile game: Blunderbubb!

Available now for download!

App Store: https://apps.apple.com/us/app/blunderbubb/id1611223311
Google Play Store (Lite version): https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.smilingquarter.bubble

Follow us on your social media platform of choice to stay up to date on our latest announcements and updates!

Website: https://smilingquarter.com
Twitter: https://twitter.com/smilingquarter
Facebook: https://facebook.com/smilingquarter
Instagram: https://instagram.com/smilingquarter
